query:
SELECT po.id, po.customerOrderNumber, po.status, po.updatedAt,
       sc.status as stageCheckStatus, sc.completedAt as stageCompletedAt
FROM pickingOrders po
LEFT JOIN stageChecks sc ON po.id = sc.pickingOrderId
WHERE po.customerOrderNumber = 'PED-005'
ORDER BY sc.id DESC
LIMIT 1;
